    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1953-07-21T05:30:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1953-07-21T05:30:00-05:00" n="1040"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1040">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">493.919/7–2153: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in India</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_AGV1"
                        type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Allen</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Department of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                    <note n="1" xml:id="d1040fn1">This telegram was also repeated to Bombay as
                        telegram 39.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">secret</hi>
                    </seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">New Delhi</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1953-07-21T16:00:00+05:30"
                            >July 21, 1953—4 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>147. Pursuant request from Naval Attaché for investigation, Polish vessel SS <hi
                        rend="italic">Mickiewicz</hi>, Bombay <gloss target="#t_ConGen1"
                        >ConGen</gloss> reports consignment by <gloss target="#t_GOI1"
                    >GOI</gloss>-owned Indian Rare Earths Limited to Taku Bar, China of 2,248 pounds
                    “foreign” thorium nitrate valued rupees 40,500. <hi rend="italic"
                        >Mickiewicz</hi> departed Bombay July 17 for Colombo. Embassy requested
                    urgent clarification facts shipment from <gloss target="#t_GOI1">GOI</gloss> and
                    will cable results.</p>
                <p>Bombay requested clarify word “foreign” and provide Department and Embassy with
                    any additional information available on subject.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_AGV1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Allen</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
